# The image is COPY-only: the build context needs nothing but the prebuilt
# `quip-faucet` binary (staged at the repo root by CI / a local cargo build).
# Ignore everything, then re-include just the binary. A top-level negation like
# this is reliable; negating a path inside an excluded dir (e.g. target/) is not.
*
!quip-faucet
